en.title: Philippines QP Wearers Sergio Ortiz-Luis JR, Ambassador Donald Dee And Congressman Antonio Roman
en.content:
L- R :  SERGIO ORTIZ-LUIS JR. Chairman/Treasurer 
of the Philippine Chamber of Commerce & Industry, 
Filipino Ambassador DONALD DEE to China & 
Special Envoy of the President on Trade Negotiation 
and Jeremy
Sharing the benefits of using Scalar Energy products
and the science behind it.
Action always speaks louder than words, 
Fusion Excel demos has NEVER fail to 
impress anyone.
Congressman Antonio Roman, an avid golfer and 
NOW a firm believer of Fusion Excel products.
